inet.ipaddr

Class AddressComparator.CountComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • inet.ipaddr.AddressComparator
      • inet.ipaddr.AddressComparator.CountComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<AddressItem>
    Enclosing class:
    AddressComparator

    public static class AddressComparator.CountComparator
extends AddressComparator
    CountComparator first compares two address items by count, first by bit count for dissimilar items, AddressItem.getBitCount(), then by count of values for similar items, (AddressItem.getCount()) and if both match, defers to the address item values for comparison. Also see AddressComparator.ValueComparator
